View all watch options   https://tryguys.com/movie 

...
Don't forget to get your tickets to the Virtual World Premiere of Behind The Try https://tryguys.com/movie on 12.18.20! Join us on the red carpet from the comfort of your own home for an evening of exclusive interviews, a special Chat Q&A with all 4 of us, guest appearances, live performances, and more! All ticket options include an extended 3-month rental of the Behind The Try Documentary along with options for a signed DVD/Blu-Ray, signed limited edition Vinyl, and exclusive t-shirt! In this episode of #TryGuys Game Time, the guys host a social media roast where they skewer and joke about each other's worst Instagrams, tweets, and posts. #TGGT

Support us! http://www.patreon.com/tryguys. Join our Patreon to get videos a day early, plus, livestreams, chatrooms, BTS footage, exclusive merchandise, and more!
